timing_report_...per_input_slew(25.10)  timing_report_...per_input_slew(25.10)

Name
       timing_report_drv_per_frequency_per_input_slew

Syntax
       timing_report_drv_per_frequency_per_input_slew

       {true | false}

       Default: false

       Enables frequency dependent DRV lookup from a library.

       When  set  to true, the software will enable the report_constraint com-
       mand to honor max_transition or max_capacitance limit after  worst-cas-
       ing due to the following cases:

              * One-dimensional  frequency  DRV commands, such as, setMaxTran-
                PerFreq or setMaxCapPerFreq.

              * Two-dimensional  maximum  transition   or   capacitance   fre-
                quency/electro-migration tables.

              * Other   frequency   independent   DRV   limit  sources,  e.g.,
                set_max_transition from the SDC or library limit.

       To set this global variable, use the set command.

